uav.generic.module.comm

Class DataAcquisitionS2DK

  • java.lang.Object
    • uav.generic.module.comm.DataAcquisition
      • uav.generic.module.comm.DataAcquisitionS2DK
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HTTPRequest

    public class DataAcquisitionS2DK
extends DataAcquisition
implements HTTPRequest
    The class models all MOSA and IFA system communication with Autopilot. Using the UAV-S2DK that use the DroneKit.
    Since:
    version 4.0.0
    See Also:
    DataAcquisition, HTTPRequest, DataAcquisition, HTTPRequest
